cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the design and training of CNNs for face recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also explores questions related to deep learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it discusses the impact of label noise on performance and the need for alignment in face recognition.
